# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — Breach Response Runbook (Canadian financial)

> **This is a starting-point template, not legal advice.** Financial-
> services breaches can simultaneously trigger PIPEDA reporting,
> FINTRAC suspicious-transaction reporting (if the incident touches
> illicit-activity indicators), and provincial-securities-regulator
> notification expectations. Counsel involvement is required from
> the moment a breach is suspected.

